      "text": "set %img% = \u0022photo.png\u0022 as image/gif strict",
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "indent": 0,
      "comment": "A path-backed image reads nothing at the set, so a strict mismatch does NOT\nfail here \u2014 it is deferred to byte-materialization (first content load). The\nset itself is clean; the throw-at-load is covered by the C#\nLazyPathHandleTests.BytesAsync_StrictKindMismatch_ThrowsAtLoad. Requires the\ncommitted photo.png fixture.",
